The Lajestic Vantrashell of Lob was the guardian of "God's Final Message to his Creation," and he sold Arthur Dent and Fenchurch tickets when they went to look at it and told them to keep to the left. He was also riding a little scooter. He was described as a "little man in a strange hat." From Chapter 40, page 183, So Long, and Thanks for All the Fish

He owned the Quentulous Stone of Firefram until Wowbagger Ultrajax stole it from him.References

